<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Tapi, Ahjussi siapa?</font>

194
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

195
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:21,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak kenal Ahjussi.</font>

196
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:23,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahjussi kenal aku?</font>

197
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu sekali...</font>

198
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:38,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku...</font>

199
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:42,040
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernah melihatmu.</font>

200
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:44,380
<font color=#FFFF00>- Begitukah?
- Aku...</font>

201
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:49,510
<font color=#FFFF00>...boleh memelukmu?</font>

202
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia adikmu?</font>

203
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:27,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan memanggilnya "Ahjussi",
panggil saja "Orabeoni".</font>

204
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:30,240
<font color=#FFFF00>"Orabeoni"?</font>

205
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:35,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah jauh-jauh kemari, mestinya temui ibumu sekalian.</font>

206
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:40,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, iya. Chun Soo Orabeoni bilang akan datang.</font>

207
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Orabeoni!</font>

208
00:19:51,610 --> 00:19:53,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo, Kko Mool.</font>

209
00:19:55,150 --> 00:19:56,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Nah... ayo.</font>

210
00:20:12,540 --> 00:20:15,240
<font color=#FFFF00>- Lee Sun-ah?
- Ayo kita sapa Ibumu,</font>

211
00:20:16,210 --> 00:20:17,710
<font color=#FFFF00>dengan masuk ke dalam.</font>

212
00:20:21,110 --> 00:20:24,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, ampuni aku, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

213
00:20:27,650 --> 00:20:29,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kemari karena merindukan keluargaku.</font>

214
00:20:29,910 --> 00:20:33,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong ampuni aku. Kumohon.</font>

215
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:37,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Seseorang tidak mungkin mendadak begitu berani.</font>

216
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa...</font>

217
00:20:41,710 --> 00:20:43,610
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang membuatmu nekat?</font>

218
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:50,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti menjadi sangat dekat dengan Daebi.</font>

219
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:56,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Mo... mohon ampuni aku, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

220
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:05,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebi memberimu hadiah berharga, 'kan?</font>

221
00:21:12,710 --> 00:21:15,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya, aku juga akan memberimu hadiah.</font>

222
00:21:15,910 --> 00:21:18,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana rasanya setelah bertemu lagi dengan keluargamu?</font>

223
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:26,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan hanya nyawaku,</font>

224
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:29,940
<font color=#FFFF00>namun nyawa seluruh keluargaku di tangan Eureushin.</font>

225
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:33,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon ampuni aku kali ini saja.</font>

226
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Eureushin...</font>

227
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan pernah...</font>

228
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:43,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan pernah mengkhianati Eureushin lagi!</font>

229
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:48,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon ampuni aku. Mohon ampuni aku kali ini.</font>

230
00:21:50,010 --> 00:21:51,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Ampunilah aku.</font>

231
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:10,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menemuimu lagi secepatnya di istana,</font>

232
00:22:11,910 --> 00:22:13,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha.</font>

233
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:24,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda baik-baik saja, Cheonha?</font>

234
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

235
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:31,310
<font color=#FFFF00>...hanya sedang bermimpi, 'kan?</font>

236
00:22:32,810 --> 00:22:33,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

237
00:22:50,940 --> 00:22:52,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau melihat Lee Sun?</font>

238
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:56,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bersama Dae Mok.</font>

239
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang untuk menemui ibu dan adiknya,</font>

240
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:00,810
<font color=#FFFF00>namun ketahuan oleh Dae Mok.</font>

241
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:04,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika bukan berkat Lee Sun,</font>

242
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:07,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok pasti sudah...</font>

243
00:23:09,010 --> 00:23:11,110
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengenaliku lagi.</font>

244
00:23:16,810 --> 00:23:19,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku merasa bersalah pada Lee Sun.</font>

245
00:23:20,710 --> 00:23:22,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika bukan karena aku,</font>

246
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:25,980
<font color=#FFFF00>dia pasti bisa bersama keluarganya sekarang.</font>

247
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:31,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa bicara padanya?</font>

248
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:37,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya bisa mengirim pesan rahasia untuk meminta bertemu dia.</font>

249
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:46,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa kau sampaikan sesuatu pada Orabeoni itu?</font>

250
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:49,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Di hari pertama bulan depan, aku akan menemuinya pukul 8 malam.</font>

251
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:53,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau berencana menemui Lee Sun?</font>

252
00:23:53,340 --> 00:23:56,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Tindakan bodoh sekali masuk ke kandang Singa!</font>

253
00:23:56,010 --> 00:23:57,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun...</font>

254
00:23:58,040 --> 00:24:01,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...berlutut pada Dae Mok, mohon diampuni nyawanya.</font>

255
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:06,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa membiarkan Lee Sun begitu saja.</font>

256
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:12,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika masuk ke istana,</font>

257
00:24:12,710 --> 00:24:15,340
<font color=#FFFF00>ada banyak mata dan telinga.</font>

258
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:19,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertahankan identitasmu sebagai Kepala Pedagang sekuat mungkin.</font>

259
00:24:21,740 --> 00:24:22,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

260
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:38,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebi Mama menghargai keputusanmu...</font>

261
00:24:38,840 --> 00:24:41,240
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mengirim tandu.</font>

262
00:24:41,810 --> 00:24:44,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersiaplah memasuki istana.</font>

263
00:24:44,710 --> 00:24:47,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Dayang istana selamanya akan menjadi wanita Raja.</font>

264
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:49,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingat itu di kepalamu.</font>

265
00:24:50,540 --> 00:24:52,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Mama-nim.</font>

266
00:24:52,980 --> 00:24:54,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Asshi.</font>

267
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:57,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi ini?</font>

268
00:25:00,810 --> 00:25:03,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim! Doryongnim!</font>

269
00:25:03,210 --> 00:25:04,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Chun Soo Doryongnim?</font>

270
00:25:05,710 --> 00:25:09,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim, tolong hentikan Ga Eun Asshi kita. Ya?</font>

271
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:11,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

272
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:12,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Asshi mengatakan...</font>

273
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:16,110
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia akan memasuki istana dan menjadi dayang.</font>

274
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

275
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikut aku.</font>

276
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah!</font>

277
00:26:14,710 --> 00:26:15,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah!</font>

278
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:24,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah!</font>

279
00:26:35,940 --> 00:26:39,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah!</font>

280
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah. Ga Eun-ah!</font>

